How is it?
If there's anything you're concerned about...

It's amazing...!!
You can't see the damage at all!

Thank you very much.
Your swift response was a great help.

This is the work of a professional...!
I really appreciate it, but how should I express it...?

Don't mention it... Just seeing Tsukioka-san
give a wonderful performance is enough.

Leave it to me then!
I'll make sure it's an amazing live performance!

That's reassuring.
But first, let's prepare for the live show.

I've got the hang of it, so I won't make the
same mistake again...! I'm a professional too!
